          alt="Custom metal and wood privacy fence Maui by Great General LLC"
          loading="lazy"
          width="800"
          height="600"
        />
        <figcaption>Privacy Fence · Custom metal &amp; wood panel system</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="photo-card">
        <img
          src="/images/metal-fab-fence-2.jpg"
          alt="Custom metal fencing installation Maui residential property by Great General LLC"
          loading="lazy"
          width="800"
          height="600"
        />
        <figcaption>Metal Fencing · Residential property, Maui</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="photo-card">
        <img
          src="/images/metal-fab-roof.jpg"
          alt="Standing seam metal roof installation Maui oceanfront property by Great General LLC"
          loading="lazy"
          width="800"
          height="600"
        />
        <figcaption>Standing Seam Metal Roof · Oceanfront property, Maui</figcaption>
